name: Vex Aeterna
description: Vex Aeterna is a gamified staking project featuring 404 tokens to create a more rewarding in-game experience. The project takes place in a world of space conquest, where a new form of energy has been discovered: Vex. Vex comes from stone found only on other planets. To collect these $VEX, you need to send your ship out for several days. The Vex Aeterna project tends to become a kind of special launchpad for all kinds of crypto projects.
